    "description": "Race high speed bio-refuse <strong>SHELLs</strong> through a dark future ruled by omni-corps and overrun with fleshy abominations. <strong>Racing Horror</strong> from Future Reality Softworks. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/693ad7191c66d6eba5cf4a32bd4dde0d.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/693ad7191c66d6eba5cf4a32bd4dde0d.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/693ad7191c66d6eba5cf4a32bd4dde0d.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>6-DOF Drift</strong><br>Experience the next dimension of anti-gravity racing: full 6-DOF flight and aerial drifting!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/08d3519d4d4913bbcdb14a12acca01ad.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/08d3519d4d4913bbcdb14a12acca01ad.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/08d3519d4d4913bbcdb14a12acca01ad.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>SHELLs</strong><br>Unlock and select from a spectrum of SHELLs - each with their own unique look, feel, and perks.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/467d29bd3adc2f8ae31d802515c34764.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/467d29bd3adc2f8ae31d802515c34764.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/467d29bd3adc2f8ae31d802515c34764.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>ML-AI</strong><br>Machine Learning (ML) based Artificial Intelligence (AI) provides for nail-biting, frenetically paced races.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/7741d69b772d29994b294c1505f04ca6.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/7741d69b772d29994b294c1505f04ca6.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/7741d69b772d29994b294c1505f04ca6.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Difficulty</strong><br>Multiple difficulty modes available with increasingly challenging AI: Rookie, Medium, Organ Donor, and Death Cult.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/478dd88c9520877062ca74bece2fd089.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/478dd88c9520877062ca74bece2fd089.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/478dd88c9520877062ca74bece2fd089.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Rumble Pack Engaged</strong><br>Feel the hum of your SHELL, the chop of the air, and the crackle of gamma-rays in your palms with integrated rumble support.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/bdac6bdd7248245ae965f03be4c9532f.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/bdac6bdd7248245ae965f03be4c9532f.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/bdac6bdd7248245ae965f03be4c9532f.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Future Reality OS</strong><br>Heart rate too high? Sweat pouring down your face? Cool down from the circuit with Future Reality OS. Delve deep into the universe of the game via the provided Terminal.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/5cb34a78aa816c24f41ebde1f43e519e.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/5cb34a78aa816c24f41ebde1f43e519e.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/5cb34a78aa816c24f41ebde1f43e519e.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Graphics</strong><br>Select through a variety of graphics options. Fans of lo-fi / retro 3D will feel at home with our faithful, almost hypnotic defaults. Future Reality also scales up to a high resolution, clean output for players who prefer a little more breathing room.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/e562b555777c7d84d6ad8fa1dfac762a.poster.avif?t=1673583245\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/e562b555777c7d84d6ad8fa1dfac762a.webm?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134050/extras/e562b555777c7d84d6ad8fa1dfac762a.mp4?t=1673583245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
